headline: Is It Time To Reconsider Humana (HUM) After Mixed Returns And DCF Upside?
summary: If you are wondering whether Humana is reasonably priced at around US$266.50 a share, you are not alone, as many investors are asking the same question about what they are really paying for. The stock is roughly flat so far in 2026 with a 0.8% return year to date. It currently sits between a 2.5% decline over the last 7 days and a 2.8% gain over the last 30 days, while the 1 year return of 8.3% and 3 year return of 42.8% highlight how sentiment has shifted over time.
